2026-04-27T08:53:04.8224912Z 41        across Android versions:
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8225595Z 42          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8226694Z 43            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8227545Z 44            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8228378Z 45          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8229228Z 46            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8230091Z 47        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8230944Z 48        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8231751Z 49        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8232374Z 50    -->
2026-04-27T08:53:04.8233017Z 51    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
