2026-04-27T08:53:04.9665149Z 43            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-27T08:53:04.9665489Z 44          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-27T08:53:04.9666054Z 45            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-27T08:53:04.9666414Z 46        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
